data.description: Welcome to your ideal investment opportunity or the perfect starter home nestled in a serene neighborhood in Macon. This charming ranch-style abode boasts 4 spacious bedrooms and 3 baths, offers over 2,000 square feet of space perfect for comfortable living. Situated in a tranquil rural setting, it promises peaceful days and star-filled nights.The inviting layout welcomes you into a cozy living space, ideal for relaxation or entertaining guests. The separate dining room is right off the kitchen, perfect for those home for the holiday moments. All bedrooms provide great space and ready for you to make it your own.     Whether you're a savvy investor seeking a promising property or a first-time homeowner, this home offers the perfect blend of charm and potential. Embrace the tranquility and endless opportunities this rural retreat has to offer.
